      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DESPICABLE KYRO (2) boasts a strong record this journey with five wins and six minors from 13 tries. Missed the frame latest (22.67) when sixth over 400m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Looks a leading chance on best. YOU WIN (3) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (25.61) in a Grade 5 at Gunnedah. Has a good record here including four wins. Has ability and can atone. FASCINATE GEORGE (4) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by one length at The Gardens in a handy 23.41 beating Maeve Baby. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and six minor placings to his credit. Leading chance again. BOMBAY (1) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
